{"tid":906600,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【APEC峯會】欲影響公報內容 4中國官員被趕出巴布亞新幾內亞外交部","createTime":"2018-11-18T06:25:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-19T13:02:16.000Z","uid":51620,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"c5926d7dcdf5ff407e0714bbdd0b7d34fe8f1306","tid":906600,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T06:25:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181118&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=58927984\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181118%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D58927984&d=6tuXhv1Op5ZcMF%2FNsQcJwEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=446932bd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181118%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D58927984&h=bc5cf9fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181118&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=58927984</a><br />\n<br />\n正在巴布亞新幾內亞（簡稱巴新）舉行的亞太經濟合作組織（APEC）峯會，籠罩在中美對峙的氣氛中。繼中國國家主席習近平與美國副總統彭斯（Mike Pence）昨各自演說中針鋒相對後，今天又傳出有中方官員試圖闖入巴新外交部長辦公室，企圖影響草擬中的峯會公報內容，惹得巴新當局驅趕4名中國官員，派出警察駐守在外交部長辦公室外。<br />\n<br />\n法新社、《澳洲人報》等媒體引述至少3名消息人士報道，有4名中國代表團成員昨天（17日）赴巴新外交部，要求會見外交部長披圖（Rimbink Pato），企圖在最後一刻影響峯會公報內容。<br />\n<br />\n披圖的發言人指出，當時披圖在辦公室內，但認為不宜單獨與中方協商，因此拒絕與他們會晤，4名中方官員因而遭逐出巴新外交部。有消息人士指出，「中方協商人士早就清楚」，披圖不願和他們見面，但執意前往披圖的辦公室。巴新外交部也表示，外長只會見其他國家的外長。<br />\n<br />\n面對法新社求證時，披圖低調回應稱此事「不構成問題」，中方代表團尚未回應此事。APEC峯會通常會達成共同聲明，但今年因中美貿易爭議激烈，官員承認恐怕無法發佈正式公報。<br />\n<br />\n台灣《蘋果日報》/《澳洲人報》"},{"pid":"6e09a4d3f80bf768a234a04e9dd8d268847e0292","tid":906600,"uid":49316,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T06:27:32.000Z","msg":"支那賤種"},{"pid":"b4a63f31e6f6daece0d3614f05c148226335a57d","tid":906600,"uid":42815,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T06:30:58.000Z","msg":"赣鳩無極限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef0626df1198a0db03a11cd198396bb692ae38ef","tid":906600,"uid":13663,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T06:31:13.000Z","msg":"支那狗又想搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"219e60e5aa58e1e76b55f0aabee8f27add596259","tid":906600,"uid":10757,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T06:32:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa1a56f94d9865496de1507d1f1b0b5c64a88d3d","tid":906600,"uid":59929,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T06:32:39.000Z","msg":"支那畜生又想柒出國際<br />\n係咪南中國海劃埋過去未通知啲力架"},{"pid":"e841618d9300b70f63ac7d192557dd485b3cd0a6","tid":906600,"uid":15880,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T06:33:56.000Z","msg":"以為去左香港咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49bf46645eef50f4307edd3cfb819d9e8a4c33d0","tid":906600,"uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T06:34:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n贏国說明你要聽"},{"pid":"dd6c19a6a62540e29db6819cccc9ea95a0e7ec8d","tid":906600,"uid":13663,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T06:34:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y3uWozx.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY3uWozx.gif&h=d83a227c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"64ca986055846392afe80c2dad1c62f29010571e","tid":906600,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T06:37:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/